pool-1-thread-4 2007-02-15 12:21:44,187 ERROR &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;qpid.server.protocol.AMQProtocolSession&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Closing connection due to: No such channel: 1 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;error code 504&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
